snippet.title: Rocket Racing Cinematic Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
It's racing without limits in Rocket Racing. In a head-to-head on the Festive Falls track, racers discover what it's going to take to secure a spot in 1st place. Choosing their own paths; flying, boosting, and flipping their way to victory. Do you have what it takes?

Rocket Racing launches in Fortnite on December 8, 2023.
